dmca.title: IBackup Trade Mark Issues
dmca.body:
Dear folks,

It has come to our attention that your product name 'IBACKUP' violates
IBackup (http://www.ibackup.com) services trademark.
We would appreciate if you would change the name of your product to
something that does not infringe upon IBackup's trademark.

Feel free to contact us for any details.

Sincerely,
